INSERT INTO
            via_btc_inscriptions_request_history (
                commit_tx_id,
                reveal_tx_id,
                inscription_request_id,
                signed_commit_tx,
                signed_reveal_tx,
                actual_fees,
                sent_at_block,
                created_at,
                updated_at
            )
            VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, NOW(), NOW())
            RETURNING
            id
